# 📌 Project Overview

AgroCast AI is an AI-powered weather forecasting system that predicts future humidity trends using a SARIMAX Time Series Forecasting model.

The system also integrates live weather data using the OpenWeather API and visualizes humidity forecasts using an interactive frontend dashboard.

This project demonstrates:

* Machine Learning deployment
* Time Series Forecasting
* Flask backend development
* API integration
* Cloud deployment
* Frontend and backend integration

---

# ✨ Features

✅ 100-Day Humidity Forecasting

✅ Live Weather Data Integration

✅ Interactive Forecast Graph

✅ AI Forecast Insights

✅ CSV Download Feature

✅ Flask REST API

✅ Cloud Deployment using Render

✅ GitHub Pages Frontend Hosting

