# ⚙️ Installation & Setup

## 1️⃣ Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/zaidrazavi/agrocast-ai.git
```

---

## 2️⃣ Open Project

```bash
cd agrocast-ai
```

---

## 3️⃣ Create Virtual Environment

### Windows

```bash
python -m venv venv
```

Activate environment:

```bash
venv\Scripts\activate
```

---

## 4️⃣ Install Dependencies

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

---

## 5️⃣ Train Model

```bash
cd backend
python train_model.py
```

---

## 6️⃣ Run Flask Backend

```bash
python app.py
```

Backend runs on:

```bash
http://127.0.0.1:5000
```

---

