# 📊 Machine Learning Model

The project uses a SARIMAX (Seasonal AutoRegressive Integrated Moving Average with eXogenous factors) model for humidity forecasting.

### Model Configuration

```python
order=(1,1,1)
seasonal_order=(1,1,1,12)
```

The model was trained using historical weather data.

